---
import MockupCotizacion from './MockupCotizacion.astro';
import MockupPagos from './MockupPagos.astro';
import MockupCFDI from './MockupCFDI.astro';
---

<section class="cord-pillars-section stripe-container reveal">
    <div class="cord-pillars-grid">
        
        <!-- Pillar 1: Cotizaciones -->
        <div class="cord-pillar-card">
            <div class="cp-content">
                <h3>Cotizaciones interactivas</h3>
                <p>Las empresas líderes optimizan sus ventas B2B con un portal interactivo donde sus clientes pueden revisar inventario, precios negociados y aprobar compras en un solo clic.</p>
                <a href="/producto/editor" class="cp-link-text">Explorar <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="12" y1="5" x2="12" y2="19"/><polyline points="19 12 12 19 5 12"/></svg></a>
            </div>
            <div class="cp-graphic">
                <MockupCotizacion />
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Pillar 2: Pagos -->
        <div class="cord-pillar-card">
            <div class="cp-content">
                <h3>Gestión de pagos B2B</h3>
                <p>Cualquier empresa puede usar Cord para monitorear el estado de su cobranza, gestionar líneas de crédito comerciales y conciliar transferencias bancarias automáticamente.</p>
                <a href="/producto/cobranza" class="cp-link-text">Explorar <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="12" y1="5" x2="12" y2="19"/><polyline points="19 12 12 19 5 12"/></svg></a>
            </div>
            <div class="cp-graphic">
                <MockupPagos />
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Pillar 3: Automatización CFDI -->
        <div class="cord-pillar-card">
            <div class="cp-content">
                <h3>Automatización de finanzas</h3>
                <p>Empresas consolidadas usan Cord para automatizar su timbrado de CFDI 4.0 al confirmar pagos, reduciendo la carga operativa y mejorando la eficiencia de su ERP actual.</p>
                <a href="/producto/cfdi" class="cp-link-text">Explorar <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="12" y1="5" x2="12" y2="19"/><polyline points="19 12 12 19 5 12"/></svg></a>
            </div>
            <div class="cp-graphic">
                <MockupCFDI />
            </div>
        </div>
        
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .cord-pillars-section {
        padding: 6rem 0;
    }
    
    .cord-pillars-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
        gap: 2rem;
    }
    
    .cord-pillar-card {
        background: #f8fafc;
        border-radius: 24px;
        box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(10,25,47,0.04), 0 10px 30px -10px rgba(10,25,47,0.03);
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        overflow: hidden;
        position: relative;
        transition: transform 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1), box-shadow 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
        min-height: 580px;
    }
    
    .cord-pillar-card:hover {
        transform: translateY(-4px);
        box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(10,25,47,0.06), 0 20px 40px -12px rgba(10,25,47,0.08);
    }
    
    .cp-content {
        padding: 2.5rem 2.5rem 1.5rem 2.5rem;
        z-index: 2;
    }
    
    .cp-content h3 {
        font-size: 1.25rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #0a192f;
        margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
        letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    }
    
    .cp-content p {
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        color: #64748b;
        line-height: 1.6;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .cp-link-text {
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #3b82f6;
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 0.25rem;
        text-decoration: none;
        transition: opacity 0.2s ease, transform 0.2s ease;
    }
    
    .cp-link-text svg {
        width: 16px;
        height: 16px;
        transform: rotate(-90deg);
        transition: transform 0.2s ease;
    }
    
    .cp-link-text:hover {
        opacity: 0.8;
    }
    
    .cp-link-text:hover svg {
        transform: rotate(-90deg) translateX(2px);
    }
    
    .cp-graphic {
        padding: 0 2rem;
        margin-top: auto;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        transform: translateY(1.5rem);
        transition: transform 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
    }
    
    .cord-pillar-card:hover .cp-graphic {
        transform: translateY(1rem);
    }

    @media (max-width: 992px) {
        .cord-pillars-grid {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }
        .cord-pillar-card {
            min-height: auto;
        }
        .cp-graphic {
            transform: translateY(1rem);
            padding-bottom: 2rem;
        }
    }
</style>

<style is:global>
    .cord-pillar-card .mock-ui {
        box-shadow: 0 12px 24px -8px rgba(10,25,47,0.1), 0 0 0 1px rgba(10,25,47,0.05) !important;
        border: none !important;
        border-radius: 12px 12px 0 0 !important;
    }
    
    .cord-pillar-card .mock-balance-card, 
    .cord-pillar-card .mock-tx-list {
        box-shadow: 0 4px 12px -4px rgba(10,25,47,0.05) !important;
        background: #ffffff !important;
        border: 1px solid rgba(10,25,47,0.03) !important;
    }
</style>
